# ============================================================================
# ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES FOR PRESALE LANDING PAGE (Vite)
# ============================================================================
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values
# For Vercel deployment, add these variables in the Vercel dashboard:
# Settings > Environment Variables
#
# NOTE: Vite uses VITE_ prefix for environment variables
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# WEB3 / WALLET CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================================

# WalletConnect Project ID (required for Web3 wallet connections)
# Get this from: https://cloud.walletconnect.com/
# Official Project ID for Presale: e6e65b93cf1c8c5ce8a07b2e90917d7b
VITE_PROJECT_ID=e6e65b93cf1c8c5ce8a07b2e90917d7b

# Alternative variable name (fallback support)
VITE_WALLET_CONNECT_ID=e6e65b93cf1c8c5ce8a07b2e90917d7b

# ============================================================================
# NOTES FOR VERCEL DEPLOYMENT
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Environment variables must start with VITE_ to be accessible
#    in the browser (Vite requirement)
#
# 2. In Vercel Dashboard:
#    - Go to Settings > Environment Variables
#    - Add VITE_PROJECT_ID with value: e6e65b93cf1c8c5ce8a07b2e90917d7b
#    - Set for: Production, Preview, Development (as needed)
#
# 3. After adding variables in Vercel:
#    - Trigger a new deployment (redeploy)
#    - Or use: vercel env pull (to sync locally)
#
# 4. If Web3 is not connecting:
#    - Check that VITE_PROJECT_ID is set in Vercel
#    - Verify the Project ID is valid at https://cloud.walletconnect.com/
#    - Check browser console for [Web3 Init - Presale] messages
#
# 5. Fallback behavior:
#    - If no Project ID is set, app uses the official fallback ID
#    - This allows the app to load even if env vars are not configured
#    - Check console for warnings: "[Web3 Init - Presale] Using fallback..."
#
# ============================================================================
